# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.0.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [1.5.1] - 2024-05-17

### Changed
- Rename property `type` into `role` in the conversation chunk schema

## [1.5.0] - 2024-05-17

### Added
- Include a new property to show if the conversation is active or not

### Changed
- Rename property `type` into `format` in the conversation chunk schema (holding type for other intention)

## [1.4.0] - 2024-05-17

### Changed
- Mark the name param of the conversation schema optional

## [1.3.0] - 2024-05-17

### Added
- Adjust conversation model to a better data structure approach

## [1.2.0] - 2024-05-16

### Added
- Include a CHANGELOG file

## [1.1.0] - 2024-05-16

### Added
- Include a new property to manage threads in the conversation model

## [1.0.0] - 2024-05-16

### Added
- Initial creation of the project.
- Initial features introduced.
